.DT
add_floating_location
Disk World creator help
add_floating_location

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
add_floating_location -  This method adds a new floating location for a terrain.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
int add_floating_location(string terrain,
string file,
int * co_ords,
int level)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^terrain%^RESET%^ - the terrain name
%^BOLD%^file%^RESET%^ - the file name
%^BOLD%^co_ords%^RESET%^ - the coordinates for the location (either a single coordinate
or 2 forming a bounding rectangle)
%^BOLD%^level%^RESET%^ - the level of this location
.EI

.SH Returns
.SI 5
1 if it succeeds, 0 if it fails (wrong coordinates or location
already present).EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/obj/handlers/terrain_handler.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This method adds a new floating location for a terrain.
.EP

.SH See also
.SP 5 5
add_fixed_location()

.EP

